https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/915IkZrsFPJFlzgsAbqrHhlMP5s.jpg The story of the longest commercial thoroughfare in America. As both neighborhood main street and transcontinental highway, Colfax Avenue provides a telling reflection of the people and events that shaped metropolitan Denver. Along the banks of this concrete river, the link between history and destiny can be discovered. Colfax Avenue: Main Street Colorado
